要推動更多香港學生到內地交流，甚至讓中學生到內地升學，陳寶生表示要視乎特區政府的決策，他相信這方面是可行的。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀得呢啲多嘅大多數到最後都係反支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做老千的先決條件，就係連自己都呃埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dc9316e138e2c20ff438228c7c4b79f6ab973d","tid":445012,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:37:33.000Z","msg":"好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073389beb8aa4c695457f82ba650aab2b9ea2ff2","tid":445012,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:43:28.000Z","msg":"好快港苦會宣佈輸入大6紅色老師來取代香港班黃絲老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}